title: Grateful Dead Live at Park West Ski Resort on 1987-08-20
lineage: Cassette Master (Nakamichi CR-7A) > Tascam DA-3000 (DSF 1-bit/5.8 MHz) >KORG AudioGate 4 > Samplitude Pro X3 Suite > FLAC/24
description:
Set 1

Big Boss Man-> Promised Land, Dire Wolf, Minglewood Blues, Row Jimmy, It's All Over Now, Loser, Cassidy, When Push Comes To Shove

Set 2

China Cat Sunflower-> I Know You Rider, Women Are Smarter, Ship of Fools, Truckin'-> Smokestack Lightning-> Drums-> Jam-> The Wheel-> Gimme Some Lovin'-> All Along The Watchtower-> Stella Blue-> Sugar Magnolia, E: The Mighty Quinn

reviews.review_text: 30 years i cant believe it took 30 years for this full soundboard to surface. Thank you!

Great Show, Great Recording My second show and one of my favorite memories. I drove cross country from New York to California in 3 days and somehow managed to take this show in. Fantastic show and ended up in some kind fellow's hot tub afterwards and enjoyed his extensive tape collection. Good times!

The show and the scene were super mellow and the setting could not have been more beautiful.
